children.name: fnTrapDemoUpdateConfig
children.description: This trap indicates that the FGT requests new configuration from management application, including FortiManager. When management application receives this trap, it should push device configuration to FGT. So this trap should be used very carefully, it causes FGT configuration being overwritten by the configuration received from management application.
